title: The Real Housewives Of Atlanta S07E05 Friend Or Faux HDTV-MegaJo

Claudia gets settled into her new life in Atlanta with Kenya's help and also begins to open up about her troubled family history. Meanwhile, Kandi makes plans to put her old house on the market but is shocked once she and Todd uncover its alarming condition. Cynthia's frustration concerning her defunct friendship with NeNe hits a peak, causing her to vent to her mom and sister.
